msgid ""
"``AWS SSM Session`` (no key needed) or ``SSH over SSM`` (key pair "
"required)."
msgstr ""
"``AWS SSM Session``\\ (키 불필요) 또는 ``SSH over SSM``\\ (키 페어 필요)"
"."

#: ../../usage.rst:26
msgid "Username"
msgstr "Username"

#: ../../usage.rst:27
msgid "Login user for **SSH over SSM** mode, e.g. ``ec2-user``."
msgstr "**SSM을 통한 SSH** 모드의 로그인 사용자, 예: ``ec2-user``."

#: ../../usage.rst:28
msgid "AWS Connection Auth"
msgstr "AWS Connection Auth"

#: ../../usage.rst:29
msgid ""
"``Use AWS Profile``, ``Static Access Key / Secret``, or ``Retrieve from "
"KeePass``."
msgstr ""
"``Use AWS Profile``, ``Static Access Key / Secret``, 또는 "
"``Retrieve from KeePass``."

#: ../../usage.rst:31
msgid "SSH Auth Method *(SSH-over-SSM only)*"
msgstr "SSH Auth Method *(SSM을 통한 SSH 전용)*"

#: ../../usage.rst:32
msgid ""
"``Manual Input / Private Key Path`` (or Vault) or ``Retrieve from "
